<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Congratulations! Your Vendor Application Has Been Approved</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            color: #2e7d32;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2e7d32;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #2e7d32;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta {
            background-color: #2e7d32;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .features {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .feature-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        .feature-item:before {
            content: "✓";
            color: #2e7d32;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">Your Business Platform</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Congratulations {{ownerName}}!</h2>
        
        <p>We're pleased to inform you that your vendor application for <span class="highlight">{{businessName}}</span> has been approved!</p>
        
        <p>You can now access your vendor dashboard to start managing your business on our platform.</p>
        
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta">Go to Vendor Dashboard</a>
        
        <p>Here's what you can do now:</p>
        
        <ul class="features">
            <li class="feature-item">Add and manage your products</li>
            <li class="feature-item">View and respond to customer inquiries</li>
            <li class="feature-item">Track your business performance</li>
            <li class="feature-item">Update your business information</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>New features coming soon:</strong></p>
        <ul class="features">
            <li class="feature-item">Advanced analytics dashboard</li>
            <li class="feature-item">Promotional tools</li>
            <li class="feature-item">Inventory management system</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>To get started, please do a fresh login using your existing credentials. You'll be taken directly to your vendor dashboard.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at {{supportEmail}}.</p>
        
        <p>Welcome aboard and happy selling!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The Vendor Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>© {{currentYear}} Your Business Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>